Deployment Notice

If you deploy this platform publicly, you must:

  1. Display a link to the complete source code in the platform UI.
  2. Retain all copyright notices and this license file.
  3. License any modifications under AGPLv3 or a compatible license.
  4. Not remove or obscure any attribution to the original author.

